Challenge: “Roller Derby Chic Extravaganza hunty 💅🏻” from @lecherros, thank you! 💝
.
Never trust a girl on 8 wheels with a smile 😉 Meet Strawberry Jam of the Seaside Siren Rollergirls! I had so much fun putting this look together, plus I got to put on my skating gear again! Can’t wait to continue learning how to roller skate with @constancemicaela but for now, dressing up will have to do 🙈
@lecherros HELL YEAH I HAVE THE SHOES!!!! THANK FAM ❤️❤️❤️
OMGAHHHHHHH you actually have the shoes!!!! Hella knocked it out of the park!!! 😍😍😍
you look amazing. can't wait to skate with you again! <3
